'''Tirsa Wargear''', headquartered on [[Tirsa]], was a vehicle manufacturer.<ref name="WC" /> During the [[Galactic War]], they produced a large number of [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]] models including the [[Capital (landspeeder)|Capital]], [[Champion (landspeeder)|Champion]], [[Contender]], [[Elite (landspeeder)|Elite]], [[Paramount (landspeeder)|Paramount]], [[Pinnacle]], [[Premier (landspeeder)|Premier]], [[Prime (landspeeder)|Prime]], and [[Victor]].<ref name="TOR" /> During the era of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] rise to power, Tirsa Wargear manufactured the [[Leviathan Submersible Carrier|''Leviathan''-class Submersible Carrier]]. They were ordered to shut down their weapons productions in the early years of the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]], but stayed in business selling spare parts. They were eventually shut down completely by the Empire.<ref name="WC" />

